      <div class="banner-content-wrapper">
                  <h1>Het Grote Vogelweekend</h1>
                
      </div>
    </div>
    
      <div class="field field--name-field-subsite-body field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-container-small paragraph-only-margin paragraph paragraph--type--layout-1-col paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--layout_1_col--80385">
            <div class="layout layout--onecol">
    <div  class="layout__region layout__region--content">
        <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph paragraph--type--image paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--image--109763">
          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
          
            <div class="field field--name-field-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--has-hover media--type-image media--view-mode-tablet" oncontextmenu="return false;">
  
      
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Afbeelding</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/tablet/public/2026-01/Het%20Grote%20Vogelweekend%202026%20Infographic%201200x480%20%282%29.jpg?itok=izWoEspa" width="1016" height="406" alt="Het Grote Vogelweekend Top 3" class="image-style-tablet" />


</div>
          </div>

          <div class="media--caption">
        
            <div class="field field--name-field-media-author field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Natuurpunt</div>
      
      </div>
      </article>
</div>
      
      </div>
      </div>
  <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-center paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--text--99531">
          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
            <div class="paragraph__text-wrapper">
    
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p class="paragraph--intro" data-path-to-node="3,0">Het Grote Vogelweekend 2026 was een recordeditie! Met maar liefst 76.342 tellers (+33%) was dit de op één na grootste editie ooit. De resultaten zijn verrassend: de pimpelmees verovert voor het eerst een plek in de top drie, terwijl het aantal <b data-path-to-node="7,0" data-index-in-node="268"><strong>huismussen</strong></b> in onze tuinen helaas jaar na jaar afneemt. Benieuwd naar alle cijfers en de belangrijkste inzichten?</p>
<p class="paragraph--intro"><a class="button--orange" href="https://www.natuurpunt.be/publicaties/rapport-het-grote-vogelweekend-2026">Lees het vogelrapport 2026</a></p>
<p class="paragraph--intro">Afspraak voor volgend jaar: <b data-path-to-node="7,2" data-index-in-node="94"><strong>zaterdag 30 en zondag 31 januari 2027</strong></b>. Noteer het alvast in je agenda!</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
      </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

    </div>
</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-container-wide paragraph-only-margin paragraph paragraph--type--layout-3-col paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--layout_3_col--106870">
          
  <div class="layout layout--threecol">
    <div class="layout--grid">
              <div  class="layout__region layout__region--first">
            <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-image-position-left-above paragraph paragraph--type--cta paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--cta--106876">
          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
              <a href="https://www.natuurpunt.be/natuurinfo/downloads/cursus-vogels-in-vlaanderen">
      <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <div class="cta--content-wrapper">
                  <h2>Online Cursus</h2>
                
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-cta-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>In Vlaanderen kan je meer dan 300 vogelsoorten spotten! Wil je ze leren kennen? Start nu met onze <strong>gratis online cursus Vogels in Vlaanderen</strong> en<strong> </strong>ontdek de rijke natuur in je buurt.</p>
</div>
      
              </div>
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-cta-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--has-hover media--type-image media--view-mode-fixed-5-6" oncontextmenu="return false;">
  
      
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Afbeelding</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/fixed_5_6/public/2026-02/CursusVogelsInVlaanderen_Thumbnail.jpg?h=7ff807d0&amp;itok=Ij8Fbjfd" width="620" height="744" alt="vogels in vlaanderen" class="image-style-fixed-5-6" />


</div>
          </div>

          <div class="media--caption">
        
            <div class="field field--name-field-media-author field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Natuurpunt</div>
      
      </div>
      </article>
</div>
      
    </div>
      </a>
        </div>
      </div>

        </div>
      
              <div  class="layout__region layout__region--second">
            <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-image-position-left-above paragraph paragraph--type--cta paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--cta--110899">
          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
              <a href="https://www.natuurpunt.be/natuurinfo/downloads/download-je-tuinvogelposter">
      <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <div class="cta--content-wrapper">
                  <h2>Vintage vogelposter</h2>
                
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-cta-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Herken je alle vogels? Download onze poster met de&nbsp;<strong>meest voorkomende vogels</strong> in Vlaanderen of word lid van Natuurpunt en ontvang hem bij je <strong>welkomstpakket</strong>.&nbsp;</p>
</div>
      
              </div>
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-cta-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--has-hover media--type-image media--view-mode-fixed-5-6" oncontextmenu="return false;">
  
      
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Afbeelding</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/fixed_5_6/public/2024-11/HGV25_Website_Vogelposter_mockup.png?h=64783bb2&amp;itok=KFJvhdHN" width="620" height="744" alt="Vogelposter" class="image-style-fixed-5-6" />


</div>
          </div>

          <div class="media--caption">
        
            <div class="field field--name-field-media-author field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Natuurpunt</div>
      
      </div>
      </article>
</div>
      
    </div>
      </a>
        </div>
      </div>

        </div>
      
              <div  class="layout__region layout__region--third">
            <div class="paragraph-background-none paragraph-image-position-left-above paragraph paragraph--type--cta paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--cta--106872">
          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
              <a href="https://winkel.natuurpunt.be/het-grote-vogelweekend">
      <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <div class="cta--content-wrapper">
                  <h2>Natuurpunt Winkel</h2>
                
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-cta-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Maak deze winter van je tuin een warme plek voor vogels met <strong>10% korting</strong> op alle vogelproducten en planten in de Natuurpunt Winkel, met de kortingscode <strong>TEL2026</strong>.</p>
</div>
      
              </div>
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-cta-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--has-hover media--type-image media--view-mode-fixed-5-6" oncontextmenu="return false;">
  
      
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Afbeelding</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/fixed_5_6/public/2025-12/NatuurpuntWinkem_Thumbnail.jpg?h=7ff807d0&amp;itok=sbJtUnLZ" width="620" height="744" alt="Natuurpunt Winkel korting" class="image-style-fixed-5-6" />


</div>
          </div>

          <div class="media--caption">
        
            <div class="field field--name-field-media-author field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Natuurpunt</div>
      
      </div>
      </article>
</div>
      
    </div>
      </a>
        </div>
      </div>

        </div>
          </div>
  </div>

    </div>
</div>
              <div class="field__item">  <div class="paragraph-background-light-blue paragraph-container-wide paragraph-only-margin paragraph paragraph--type--layout-1-col paragraph--view-mode--full" id="paragraph--layout_1_col--105565">
            <div class="layout layout--onecol">
    <div  class="layout__region layout__region--content">
