          <div class="paragraph-wrapper">
          
    
      <div class="field field--name-field-entity-embed-entities field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__items">
              <div class="field__item">
<article class="node node--type-testimonial node--view-mode-teaser node--type-testimonial--teaser node--no-sidebar">

    
  

        
    
  <div class="node__content">
    <div class="teaser--left">
      
            <div class="field field--name-field-testimonial-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item"><article class="media media--has-hover media--type-image media--view-mode-testimonial" oncontextmenu="return false;">
  
      
  <div class="field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden">
    <div class="field__label visually-hidden">Afbeelding</div>
              <div class="field__item">    <picture>
                  <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/testimonial/public/2025-12/HetGroteVogelweekend2026_Tom_Blob_4.png?itok=ExNPAYAh 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/testimonial_x2/public/2025-12/HetGroteVogelweekend2026_Tom_Blob_4.png?itok=bVB6JnF- 2x" media="all and (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px)" type="image/png" width="220" height="211"/>
              <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/testimonial/public/2025-12/HetGroteVogelweekend2026_Tom_Blob_4.png?itok=ExNPAYAh 1x" type="image/png" width="220" height="211"/>
                  <img loading="lazy" width="220" height="211" src="/sites/default/files/styles/testimonial/public/2025-12/HetGroteVogelweekend2026_Tom_Blob_4.png?itok=ExNPAYAh" alt="Tom Van Dyck" />

  </picture>

</div>
          </div>

      </article>
</div>
      
    </div>
    <div class="teaser--right">
            
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-testimonial-testimonial field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Zelfs in een kleine stadstuin kan je al iets betekenen voor vogels. Dat ondervind ik zelf in onze eigen stadstuin, die we natuurvriendelijk hebben ingericht.</p>
</div>
      
            <div class="field field--name-field-testimonial-author field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Tom Van Dyck, acteur en ambassadeur van Het Grote Vogelweekend</div>
      
    </div>
  </div>

</article>
</div>
